public abstract class MonovaluedValuedVertexTest<ValueType>
extends TargettedVertexTest
implements VertexTest

Base class for all simple tests (like contains, greater than, ...). Notice expected is used for both direct value comparison (for literals) and id check (for managed objects). This is done by asking the TargettedVertexTest#serviceRrepository if expected is a managed value
